operator[] returning a int pointer? Maybe this is what you meant:

    int* operator[](size_t y) { return &ary[y*width]; }

Then you could write:

    my2DArray[y][x]

Although better practice would be to use operator():

    int& operator[](int x, int y) { return ary[y*width+x]; }

