One can add the numbers 1 to 10 (and store it in sum) like this:

for(i = 1; i <= 10; sum += i++) ;  //empty loop body

IMHO doing this using DoNothing() is more self-documenting:

for(i = 1; i <= 10; sum += i++)
{
    DoNothing();
}

